	<text>
		<body>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Detroit</placeName>&#44; <date>February 2nd 1857</date></p>
				<p><addressee>Rev Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">Enclosed please find Dft. For &#36;12.62<lb/> <sic>intented</sic> for</p>
				<table rows="6" cols="2">
				<row>
				<cell>my one years subscription</cell>
				<cell>&#36;3.00</cell>
				</row>
				<row>
				<cell>one Prayer book <persName>M M Edg</persName></cell>
				<cell>3.50</cell>
				</row>
				<row>
				<cell>One dd Gilt &#8220;</cell>
				<cell>4.25</cell>
				</row>
				<row>
				<cell>One copy of <persName>Miss Sal.</persName> Poems sent</cell>
				<cell/>
				</row>
				<row>
				<cell> for <persName>Mr D Davies</persName></cell>
				<cell><hi rend="underline">   1.87</hi></cell>
				</row>
				<row>
				<cell/>
				<cell>&#36;12.62</cell>
				</row>
				</table>
				<p>According to the above and the books<lb/> accounted for <add>&#63;</add> remittance of<lb/> <date>Nov 1855</date> there is left in <sic>comission</sic> here</p>
				<table rows="5" cols="3">
				<row>
				<cell>1 Bible</cell>
				<cell>9.00</cell>
				<cell/>
				</row>
				<row>
				<cell>1 set Pentateuch</cell>
				<cell>16.00</cell>
				<cell/>
				</row>
				<row>
				<cell>2 prayer books &#64; 4.25</cell>
				<cell>8.50</cell>
				<cell/>
				</row>
				<row>
				<cell>2 &#8220; d 3.50</cell>
				<cell>7.00</cell>
				<cell/>
				</row>
				<row>
				<cell>6  d  20&#47;</cell>
				<cell>15.00</cell>
				<cell>&#36;55.50</cell>
				</row>
				</table>
				<p>I am about changing my residence to <placeName>N.Y.</placeName><lb/> and have left there books subject to your order<lb/> with my brother <persName>Simon</persName> successor to my establishing<lb/> here.  Please discontinue for the same reason<lb/> to send the Occident to my address &#38; acknowledge<lb/> receipt of the above under care <persName>Freedmans Brs</persName><lb/> school</p>
			<p rend="indent(11)">Yours Respectfully</p>
			<p rend="indent(11)"><persName role="author">Joseph Freedman</persName></p>
		</body>
